org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT users.* FROM users INNER JOIN members ON members.user_id = users.id INNER JOIN member_roles ON member_roles.member_id = members.id INNER JOIN roles ON roles.id = member_roles.role_id WHERE users.status = "$1" AND users.type = "$2" AND members.project_id = "$3" AND roles.assignable = "$4" AND roles.id IN ("$5", "$6", "$7", "$8", "$9") ORDER BY users.type DESC, users.firstname, users.lastname, users.id
